# index.html
Lesson Area: Displays MCQ, fill-ups, true/false questions with code snippets Input &amp; Options: Text input for fill-ups, buttons for MCQs Feedback Zone: Correct/wrong messages with empathy Motivation Panel: Inspirational quotes every 5–10 questions SpendSmart App: Hidden until course completion — includes expense form, chart, and AI insights
Purpose: 
The entry point of the web app. Defines the complete HTML structure including:
- Header with app name and streak
- Progress bar and XP counter
- Lesson display area
- Input field for fill-ups
- Options for MCQ/True-False
- Feedback and motivation sections
- SpendSmart mini-app (unlocked at the end)

Key Features:
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Semantic HTML5
- Integration of Chart.js for visualizations
- Links to all CSS and JS files
- Clean, Duolingo-inspired UI layout
